description:
We know where you can find the flavours that fit you.  If there's one thing we know it’s food delivery. It’s our mission to bring tasty food from your favourite local restaurant right to your door so you can eat good food everyday. We'll go the extra mile to make your order the greatest food experience in the world. Hungry for wood-fired pizza, a classic burger or the freshest sushi? We know the best food for every cuisine that your city has to offer. foodora is the best food delivery and take away service in your city -- so let's take the first bite!

Check if we're in your city by downloading the app.

SO WHAT’S THE DEAL?

You’re ready and waiting to eat, we’ve all been there, dreaming of thai food, eating burgers in our dreams. Here’s what we do: first choose between delivery and Pick-Up to fit food ordering seamlessly into your schedule. Pick-Up is simple -- you make your order and then collect your food from the restaurant once it’s ready. No more queuing, ever (our app is magic). If you choose delivery, our couriers will bring the food you've been lusting after right to your door. Dreams really do come true.

HOW IT WORKS

First, enter your address (home/ office/ treehouse). Then, choose your favourite restaurant and place an order. They’ll prepare your food and once it’s ready, our courier bring it to you. If you need something to watch, you can track your rider in real-time. Then you eat. Food goals.

WHAT MAKES US SPECIAL

foodora chooses your local favourites; the best food near you. Vietnamese or Italian, healthy salads or food to nurse your hangover -- your dinner will be cooked with love and care. Our riders come to your very doorstep with a smile while you save time to do something else you love. There's a cuisine and a dish to suit every moment, and we'll help you make the first bite last.

ANYTHING ELSE?

Of course your safety is important to us. We guarantee secure, simple mobile payment, so you can eat when you're hungry and pay however you like.

TALK TO US

If you’ve ordered with us before, we’d want to know what you think. Give us your food thoughts/ teenage confessionals. Let us be your notepad.
Email us at support@foodora.se

For further info, visit
www.foodora.com/

With the Pinchos app, you manage the entire restaurant experience right from your phone. Book a table, order food and drinks – and easily pay the bill at the end of your visit. Maybe you'd also like to challenge your company in a quiz? Last but not least – join our guest club The Society and start collecting rewards! Welcome to Pinchos.

Enjoy your favorite restaurants and stores, all in one place.
The Wolt app makes it easy to discover and order (almost) anything from your city. From delicious food and fresh groceries to pharmacy and pet supplies. Search by category, cuisine, restaurant or item! You can easily browse popular restaurants including McDonald's, KFC, Domino's, Pizza Hut, Papa Johns, Burger King and many more. Enjoy food delivery of burgers, pizza, sushi and other delicious items. If you prefer, you can pick up your order from the restaurant or store!

Order (almost) anything, on-demand.
Need to stock up on groceries? Can’t make it to the city? Wolt has you covered with groceries and essentials at your fingertips. Browse through the categories on Wolt and order anything, from pharmacy items to pet supplies. Anything you need, we’ve got you covered with our 40 000+ restaurants and stores. 

Top offers, only on Wolt.
Discover great offers on food, groceries and more! Browse hand-picked deals in the Wolt app and enjoy great savings. There’s offers on everything from food and groceries to electronics and homewares. Find the freshest deals in the app, including up to 50% off your order and €0 delivery fees!


Subscribe to Wolt+
If you’re looking for even bigger savings, Wolt+ is our popular subscription service offering €0 delivery fees, plus much more. As a Wolt+ member, you’ll unlock unbeatable deals and exclusive perks.

Make every occasion special with Wolt
We’ve made it easy to order and enjoy whatever you need. Get gifts for your loved ones, schedule orders for groceries and food, and save with deals on clothing and more! Wolt has you covered with everything to make moments special. Browse the selection of lovely flowers, chocolates, baked treats and more – delivered to your door in one hour or less.

Double Order
Need to order groceries and dinner? Now you can! Combine two local venues in one order with the same delivery fee. Place a Double Order and enjoy more convenience, for less!

Track every step
With every order, you can enjoy real-time tracking, and a minute-by-minute countdown. Whether you keep an eye on the tracker, or have other things to do, we'll keep you notified, so you know when your order is about to arrive.

Customer support
If something doesn’t go as planned, we’re ready to help – with customer support available 24/7. Our friendly team is there to help the 25+ countries we operate in and are ready to respond in seconds.

Payment
We think ordering Wolt should be as simple as possible. That’s why you can pay conveniently and securely with your credit card or Apple Pay. Whatever works for you.

Life simplified. Joy delivered. 
Wolt is currently available in 170+ cities located in Azerbaijan, Croatia, Cyprus, Czechia, Denmark, Estonia, Finland, Georgia, Germany, Greece, Hungary, Israel, Japan, Kazakhstan, Latvia, Lithuania, Malta, Norway, Poland,  Serbia,  Slovakia, Slovenia, Sweden. More are added all the time! Download Now and Unlock Essentials at your fingertips.

Wolt is an Editors’ Choice! 
Recognized by Apple as a top-rated app, Wolt delivers more than just food. Enjoy a seamless experience, from browsing our curated selection of restaurants to tracking your order in real-time.

Welcome to the new official McDonald’s app.

The app is filled with great offers specially tailored to you. Deals and discounts appear regularly so check back often to see what’s new.

The news section keeps you up to date with everything that’s going on in McDonald’s near you. Look here for new games and competitions.

The nutrition section provides information on our entire menu. We provide allergy advice and nutritional information on everything from the Big Mac to a single dip!

Use our restaurant finder to find your nearest McDonald’s. Filter your search based on opening hours, facilities and get directions from wherever you are.

“HESBURGER COUPONS ON YOUR PHONE? DONE!”
The Hesburger app makes it easy to have a treat. Download Hesburger’s legendary discount coupons! The app also lets you order and pay for products with ease. You’ll have a Bonus Card on your phone, giving you access to all the excellent discounts of the Bonus Club. And just a couple of clicks will show you the nearest Hesburger restaurants. And their opening hours. And the latest campaigns. And… Well, download it and you’ll see.

HOW TO MAKE THE MOST OF THE APP:

1. Use the app to join or log in to our free Bonus Club. This will give you more coupons, let you collect and spend Bonus money and enjoy all our Bonus discounts.
2. Add your credit or debit card details to the app. This will let you order and pay for products on your phone and pick them up at a restaurant (“click and collect”).

Download it now.

Enjoy your Hesburger!

Download the new Burger King Finland app! When you register for the app, in addition to the tasty benefits, you get access to the MyBK loyalty program. You collect points from all orders you purchase through the app. And with those tasty points - you can redeem rewards.

We develop the application continuously and encourage you to always update the latest version to get all the features at your disposal.

• Register for the app! You get instant access to multiple coupons and a tasty weekly benefit. 
• Access to MyBK benefit program where you collect points for purchasing through the app.
• You can pre-order from a restaurant you prefer and pick up your order at an agreed time. No lines and no waiting!

Save money by rescuing goods from your favourite shops. ResQ Club is a service that connects users with local restaurants, cafés, grocery stores, and florists offering surplus food and flowers at discounted prices. These items are still of good quality but would otherwise go to waste. 

Getting Started:

1. Download the App.
2. Browse Offers: Explore available deals on a map or in a list format.
3. Make a Purchase: Select the items you wish to rescue and pay securely through the app.
4. Pick Up Your Order: Collect your items from the venue within the specified pickup time.

By using ResQ, you contribute to reducing food and flower waste, support local businesses, and enjoy quality products at lower prices. 

Get the most out of the ResQ Club app:

1. Mark your favourite venues for effortless browsing and get notified of their latest offers.
2. Enable notifications for the ResQ app so you never miss deals near you.
3. Look for the Best of ResQ symbol – these partners are top-rated by our community!

More about ResQ Club:

Website: https://resq-club.com/
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/resqclub/

We would love to hear your feedback! If you need help or have suggestions, email us at info@resq-club.com.

Picnic-äppi – kanta-asiakkuus taskussasi

Picnic-äppi on Picnic-ravintoloiden oma kanta-asiakassovellus, jossa saldo kasvaa syödessä. Mitä useammin käyt, sitä enemmän hyödyt! Kertyneen Picnic-saldon voit käyttää maksamiseen kaikissa Picnic-ravintoloissa.

Äpistä löydät myös kausittain vaihtuvat edut – esimerkiksi kuukauden patongin aina edullisempaan hintaan. Lisäksi saat käyttöösi sesongin mukaisia kuponkietuja niin kahvista kuin ruokaostoksistakin.

Piipahda patongille, poikkea perunalle.
Picnic – aina helpoin valinta."

Cluby is a free membership card for restaurants, bars, cafes & nightclubs.

With Cluby, you can connect with your favorite places and enjoy membership benefits & perks. You can also easily buy lunch & coffee passes, entrance tickets, VIP-cards and other products.

Inspiroivat reseptit, omat ruokasuunnitelmat ja polku ruokakauppaan löytyvät nyt samasta paikasta – Yhteishyvä Ruoka -sovelluksesta. Kun arkesi helpottuu, ruoanlaitto on hauskempaa kuin koskaan!

TUHANSIA LAADUKKAITA RESEPTEJÄ

- Inspiroivia, laadukkaita ja ammattilaisten testaamia reseptejä arkeen ja juhlaan. 
- Reseptit huomioivat satokauden ja juhlapäivät.
- Runsaasti kasvisruokia, suomalaisia klassikoita ja kansainvälisiä makuja.
- Ihania makeita reseptejä ja leipureiden lempiherkkuja.

SUJUVAN ARJEN RUOKASUUNNITELMAT

- Suosikkireseptit helposti talteen omiin kansioihin.
- Ruokatoimittajan laatima ruokalista vuoden jokaiselle viikolle.
- Omat ruokasuunnitelmat näppärästi koko viikoksi tai vaikka mökkiviikonloppua varten.

POLKU RUOKAKAUPPAAN

- Reseptien ainekset kätevästi suoraan kauppalistalle.
- Annosmääriä ja tuotteita on helppo muokata tilanteen ja mieltymysten mukaan. 
- Kaikkien reseptien ainekset ovat ostettavissa S-ryhmän kaupoista.

RAUHOITTAVA KOKKAUSTILA

- Selkeät valmistusohjeet askel kerrallaan.
- Puhelimen näyttö ei pimene kesken kokkauksen.
- Ääniohjauksella valmistusvaiheesta toiseen koskematta ruutuun jauhoisin käsin!

Fika Club is Espresso House's app, where you can enjoy Fika Moments while earning Fika Points!

Inspired by Sweden's cherished tradition of Fika, your first Fika is on us when you sign up in the app. Plus, as a Fika Club member, you can:

- Receive personalized offers: the offers are tailored just for you
- Collect Fika Points: you earn Fika Points when you shop, top-up, or complete Fika Fun challenges
- Redeem for rewards: you get to choose your rewards and enjoy your Fika moments just how you like them
- Preorder in the app: skip the queue and have more time for your Fika moments

Nappaa puhelimeesi Taco Bellin kuponkiedut ja kerää pisteitä tilauksistasi!

Ready, set… taco!
Taco Bell sovelluksella voit tehdä ja maksaa tilauksia useilla maksutavoilla, helposti ja jonottamatta.
Nauti ruoka paikan päällä tai nappaa takeawayna mukaasi!

Parhaat kupongit löytyvät aina puhelimestasi ja voit käyttää niitä sovelluksen kautta tilatessasi.

Tilaamalla sovelluksen kautta ansaitset ostoksistasi pisteitä jokaisella kerralla. Pisteitä
kerryttämällä pääset palkintotasoille, jotka avaavat käyttöösi herkullisia etuja.

Live Más & level up!

Lataa tuhansien reseptien koti
Kun maailma on ihania ideoita tulvillaan, mistä tunnistaa sen oikean – oman arjen seuraavan luottoreseptin tai lempileivonnaisen, jonka tulee leipomaan vielä lukemattomia kertoja?
Valio sovellus on keittiösi luottoapuri, joka auttaa läpi kiireisten arkiaamujen ja ikimuistoisten juhlahetkien. Selaa tuhansia reseptejä tai personoi reseptiehdotuksesi omaan ruokavalioosi sopiviksi.

Ota käyttöön uudet toiminnallisuudet
Sovelluksen uusilla ominaisuuksilla hetkesi keittiössä soljuu eteenpäin kuin tanssi: rakenna lempiresepteistäsi viikon ruokalista ja klikkaa raaka-aineet kauppalistalle. Ja kun käyt kokkaamaan, muista laittaa päälle näppärä kokkaustila. Sen avulla etenet reseptin vaiheesta toiseen ilman turhia skrollauksia.

Inspiroidu resepteistä
Mokkapalat, uunilohi vai jotain uutta ja ihanaa? Valio sovelluksesta löydät yli 5000 Valio Koekeittiön ja yhteistyökumppaniemme testaamaa reseptiä sekä vinkit, joilla onnistut varmasti. Olitpa vasta-alkaja tai oman elämäsi huippukokki.

Kokeile rulettia
Yllättikö ruokapaniikki? Sovelluksen reseptiruletti pelastaa, kun pää lyö kauppareissulla totaalisen tyhjää – ja raaka-aineperusteinen haku helpottaa hetkinä, kun inspiraatiota metsästää oman jääkaapin ääressä.

Rakenna oma keittokirja
Digitaalinen keittokirja? Kyllä vain! Valio sovellus on kuin hyllyllinen keittokirjoja – mutta aika paljon modernimmassa muodossa. Tallenna suosikkireseptisi muistiin ja jaa bravuurisi myös ystävälle.

Tutustu tuotteisiin
Nappaa talteen tiedot klassikosta, inspiroidu uutuuksista ja tiedä, mistä ruokamaailmassa puhutaan. Joko herkutellaan?

Unlock your home's full potential with HomeID.


HomeID, formerly NutriU, is your all-in-one app for meal planning and prep, with a variety of healthy and delicious recipes to explore. It's your companion for delicious Airfryer recipes and meals - from breakfast to dinner, healthy snacks, and delightful coffee breaks. Collaborating with home cooks, professional chefs, baristas, and Philips Kitchen Appliances, HomeID elevates daily routines into enjoyable experiences with:
• A vast array of easy recipes for every meal and occasion, including snacks, main courses, desserts, brunches, hot drinks, and more. Explore a world of homemade culinary delights.
• Detailed nutritional information for each recipe, empowering you to make informed choices for yourself and your loved ones.
• Diverse culinary options catering to all preferences, such as pasta, casseroles, chicken dishes, cheesecakes, and an extensive selection of vegan and vegetarian choices.
• Instructional videos, expert advice, and integrated features for Philips kitchen appliances, covering Airfryers, coffee/espresso machines, pasta makers, blenders, juicers, Air Steam Cookers, and All-in-One Cookers.
• Tips for crafting the perfect espresso or a simple caramel latte, bringing barista-level coffee into your home.
• A community dedicated to finding joy in the small things amid busy schedules.
• Plus, you can now purchase home appliances directly from your HomeID app.


HomeID - Your Comprehensive Home Appliance App.
Maximize your capabilities with HomeID. Suitable for new appliance owners and seasoned users, HomeID unveils the full potential of your home.
Embrace simplicity in your daily life. Join us at HomeID.

Get food delivery to your doorstep from thousands of amazing local and national restaurants. Find the meal you crave and order food from restaurants easily with the Uber Eats app. Track your order in real-time.

FIND YOUR FAVOURITE FOOD & RESTAURANTS
Order food from nearby restaurants and search by cuisine, restaurant name, dish, and meal. 
Food delivery options for you to order and enjoy such as pizza, burritos, burgers, sushi, fish and chips, doughnuts and Chinese takeout.
Prefer pickup? Skip the line and reservations and choose to pick up your order instead. Choose your favourite delivery options with the Uber Eats app now.

SUBSCRIBE TO UBER ONE
For £5.99 per month, Uber One subscribers enjoy £0 delivery fee and up to 5% off orders over £15 at participating non-grocery stores (and 5% off orders over £25 at participating grocery stores) available on Uber Eats. Members are also eligible for rewards, perks, coupons, and offers. View full Uber One Terms & Conditions in app.

ORDER ALMOST ANYTHING, ANYTIME
Order household needs from your favourite pharmacies, supermarkets, and pet shops. Baby food or nappies, pharmacy needs, beauty products and cosmetics. Grocery staples like bread and milk, bananas and produce, flowers and plants, packaged foods or frozen treats. 

You can even order alcoholic drinks including beer, wine, spirits and cocktails.*

SIMPLE DELIVERY ORDERING
Pick your food order from any menu and add it to your cart with a few taps. That’s it.
Uber Eats makes it easy to order food delivery online or through the app and have it delivered by restaurants and delivery people near you.
Or, schedule your order in advance for a delivery person to pick it up later. Your choice!

ORDER FOOD AHEAD WITH PICKUP
Now you can also order food ahead for Pickup instead of just ordering delivery. Select Pickup, add food items to your cart, and skip the lines to the restaurant to get your food.

REAL-TIME ORDER TRACKING
Track your food delivery order on a map as it heads your way.
See the estimated arrival time at your address.
Get notified when your order arrives.

FIND SOME OF YOUR FAVOURITE NATIONAL RESTAURANTS
Some of our food delivery partners include: Pizza Hut, Domino’s Pizza, Burger King, Dunkin', KFC, McDonald's, Starbucks, Subway, Taco Bell,Costa Coffee, Kaspas, Gourmet Burger Kitchen, Franco Manca, Dixy Chicken, Chipotle, Chaiiwala, Amigos Burgers Shakes, Papa John’s, Krispy Kreme.  

FIND PHARMACIES, GROCERY STORES, AND MORE
Order from grocery stores such as Asda, Sainsbury Supermarket, Waitrose, The Co-op, Iceland, M&S Food, and Londis. You can also order from pharmacies such as Boots via Uber Eats, as well as from other delivery partners in the convenience and retail spaces.

ABOUT UBER EATS
Uber Eats is the way to order the food you love through an easy delivery experience. Uber Eats is available in hundreds of cities around the world. Enter your delivery address to explore restaurant and grocery delivery options near you.

AVAILABLE INTERNATIONALLY

Join others in your city who use the Uber Eats app to order from their favourite restaurants and schedule delivery.

Uber Eats is currently available in cities and metro areas including Adelaide, Amsterdam, Atlanta, Auckland, Austin, Baltimore, Brussels, Cape Town, Chicago, Dallas, Denver, Johannesburg, Glasgow, London, Los Angeles, Madrid, Melbourne, Mexico City, Miami, Milan, Nashville, New Orleans, New York, Ottawa, Paris, Philadelphia, San Diego, San Francisco, Seattle, Stockholm, Sydney, Taipei, Tokyo, Toronto, Warsaw, and Washington DC. Uber Eats helps you find food delivery around the world. Order delivery in countries around the world. See full list of available countries on our website. Uber content/messages human- or machine-translated as per device settings; accuracy not guaranteed

*Alcohol is only available in select markets. Must be at least 18 to purchase. Item availability varies by market. See the Uber Eats app for details.

Make your visit at the Jungle Juice Bar even smoother by downloading the new mobile app! By downloading the app, you can join our loyalty program. You will earn coconuts for every purchase and redeem free gifts with the collected coconuts. You can also pre-order and pay smoothies with the app which means that the products you ordered will be waiting you in our bar! Quick and effortlessly. In addition, you will find the contact information for the bars and the entire product range with the nutrition information etc. 

With the app, you get:

- Jungle Juice Bar loyalty program
- You collect coconuts for every purchase and can redeem free gifts with them 
- Targeted offers and discounts
- Pre-order opportunity
- Contact information and opening hours for bars
- Product information
- The latest news

Welcome to the Pizza Hut app!
 
Here ordering pizza is quick and easy - whether you want to order original Pizza Hut pan pizza or our other tasty pizzas. Vegan and gluten-free options are also available. In this app you will always find our best deals and contact information for our restaurants.

Mobile app – local service. Wherever you are.
 
Find and remember. With Alko’s mobile app, you have tastes from all over the world at your fingertips. Use the app to record your personal taste memories. You can make lists of the drinks you’ll serve at upcoming parties or the products you’ve found that suit your taste. This will help you to easily find your favourite products whenever you want.
 
HELP FOR CHOOSING BEVERAGES
On the mobile app, you can conveniently browse through our selection of thousands of products, perform product searches and have a closer look at additional information on each product. Handy product search filters help you to pick out a suitable beverage to complement a certain food or find Green Choice products. 
 
SCANNER FINDS PRODUCTS FAST
Use the handy barcode scanner to find a product from Alko’s selection.
 
LOCATE A STORE
Alko has a network of more than 350 stores. The mobile app will show you where to find the closest Alko store or a certain outlet or pick-up point.
 
BROWSE THE STORE SELECTION 
Alko’s extensive assortment varies by store. The app enables you to browse the products stocked on the shelves of a specific store. You can also check the availability of an individual product at different stores.

PRODUCTS COMING SOON
Have a sneak peek at next week’s upcoming products. In the product list you can check in advance product’s name, availability date, price, product category, taste type, packaging size and alcohol percentage.

LOG IN FOR A FULLER EXPERIENCE
When you are logged in, you can create lists, review individual products and chat with our customer service. You can also buy products through the mobile app.
 
EASY SHOPPING
With the app, you can buy products from your own lists or the whole selection. In addition to thousands of beverages, our selection includes high-quality accessories, such as for serving drinks and wrapping gifts.

The app is intended for people aged 18 and over. Contains information about alcohol products. The customer's age is always checked in connection with the online store order.

Read the Alko app accessibility statement on Alko's website: https://www.alko.fi/en/verkkokaupan-saavutettavuusseloste

COLLECT POINTS WITH EVERY PURCHASE AND ENJOY DELICIOUS REWARDS!

Just like our delicious treats, our app and loyalty program are baked using only the finest ingredients. Let’s see what they’re made of.

INNER CIRCLE – AN OFFER YOU CAN’T REFUSE

In our Loyalty Program you’ll enjoy:
- Delicious rewards
- Special perks and discounts
- Online orders without waiting (coming later)

Use the JOE & THE JUICE app to order your favorite juice, coffee, sandwich, or smoothie, for pick-up or delivery, and earn points on every purchase with the new Loyalty Program.

After your first app order you will get an item at no cost.* A healthy sandwich, smoothie, or salad bowl—you choose!

Still not convinced? Here are more good reasons why you are going to love the JOE & THE JUICE app:

PRE-ORDER:
- Skip the line and save time!
- Place an order in the app and it will be ready when you arrive, or choose an exact pick-up time.
- Customize food and drinks to your dietary preferences. Gluten free sandwich? Acai bowl without granola? Protein or collagen in your iced matcha? The app makes it possible.
- Track the progress of your order and receive a notification when it’s ready!

LOYALTY PROGRAM & REWARDS
Our new Loyalty Program gives you control into the way you get rewarded for your loyalty.
- Earn points with every purchase made in the app or in store using scan to pay excluding purchases made with JOE Cards, Reward Cards and Campaign cards.
- Exchange your points on your favorite juices, coffees and treats. 
- Complete fun in-app challenges to boost your points and unlock exclusive rewards.
- Level up through the Loyalty Program. The more you order, the higher your level!

Our Loyalty Program consists of 3 levels:
- GREY: Welcome Reward after your first purchase (excluding counter products, shots and water). Your journey begins here.
- YELLOW: Order 15 items per year and level up to Joe Member status. Earn +10% more points on every purchase.
- PINK: Order 50 items per year and unlock exclusive rewards you won’t find anywhere else. Earn +20% more points, plus even more treats, surprise campaigns and more.

DELIVERY
Need your brewed espresso, tropical smoothie, breakfast bundle, or sandwich delivered straight to your door? Say no more! Use Deliveroo, or order directly through the JOE app so you don’t miss out on any points.

WAIT, THERE’S MORE. USE THE APP TO:
- Find the nearest JOE & THE JUICE location.
- Scan for points when you order food and drinks at the counter.
- Reorder your favorite food and drinks with two taps. That best smoothie on the planet. Or sweet green salad.
- Receive special JOE coffee and juice offers before everyone else.
- View allergens, nutrition, and calories for each food and drink product. Gluten? Vegan? Specialty coffee order? The app has your back with whatever makes you feel good and healthy.

*To receive a complimentary item, the first app order cannot be water, shots, or counter products. Offer limited to one per credit card.

If you have any questions or feedback, you can contact customer service in the app.

For more juice, smoothie, coffee, and fast delivery, find us on Instagram @joeandthejuice or visit www.joejuice.com

Pancho Villa -sovellus tuo tarjouksia ja etuja suoraan puhelimeesi 

Hyödynnä nyt rahanarvoiset tarjoukset valitsemastasi Pancho Villa -ravintolasta tai vaikka kaikista Panchoista! Pancho Villa -sovellus tuo sinulle mahdollisuuden vastaanottaa tarjouksia ja etuja, sekä seurata viimeisimpiä tiedotteita ja uutisia. Saat ensimmäisten joukossa tiedon mitä Panchoissa tapahtuu. Samalla saat käyttöösi sähköisen lounaspassin, jolla ansaitset joka 10. lounaan ilmaiseksi. Lounaspassilla voit kerätä leimoja kaikista Pancho Villa -ravintoloista, sekä lunastaa ilmaisen lounaan mistä tahansa Panchosta! Aika Panchoo!

Voit valita tietyn Pancho Villan mitä seurata, tai voit valita minkä kaupungin Pancho Villa -ravintoloita seuraat. Sovelluksesta löytyy myös Pancho Villan menu, sekä jokaisen ravintolan lounaslistat. Tarjouksien ja etujen vastaanottaminen vaatii ilmaisen kirjautumisen, joka onnistuu myös Google- tai Apple -tunnuksilla. Lataa ja herkuttele!

Lataa Rollsin sovellus ja saat kaikki edut käyttöösi!

Ominaisuudet

Ainutlaatuiset tarjoukset aina käytössäsi. Saat sovelluksen kautta tarjoukset ja edut, jotka voit lunastaa ravintolassa.

Mitä ikinä haluat tietää Rollsista: menu, ravintolahaku, ravintosisältö- ja raaka-ainetiedot

Lisätietoa Rollsista: 
Kolme vuosikymmentä ja sata ravintolaa myöhemmin, sama reilu asenne ohjaa yrityksen toimintaa. Matkan alkutaipaleella kehitetyt hampurilaiset ovat yhä listamme suosikkeja. Jokainen annos valmistetaan koosta, mausta ja raaka-aineista tinkimättä. Laadun takeena Rollsin palveluita ja hampurilaisia koristaa Avainlippu.

Rolls. Kaikin puolin reilu.

Discover authentic street foods from around the world with Flavor Road. This comprehensive app helps you explore, track, and learn about traditional street foods through an interactive map, detailed encyclopedia, and personal food passport.
Navigate through a beautiful map interface to find street food locations across different countries and cities. Each food entry includes rich details like ingredients, flavors, cultural history, vendor stories, and dining etiquette. Filter foods by category, dietary preferences, or occasion to find exactly what you're looking for.
Build your culinary passport by marking foods as tried and adding favorites to your collection. Track your food journey with detailed statistics showing your exploration progress across different countries and food categories. Unlock achievements as you discover new foods and expand your culinary horizons.
Perfect for food enthusiasts, travelers, and anyone curious about global street food culture. Whether you're planning a trip or simply want to learn about different cuisines, Flavor Road brings the world's street food scene to your fingertips.
